{"tid":248925,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"估唔到老蕭最後都係投共","createTime":"2017-05-19T02:57:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T03:56:05.000Z","uid":80570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a318dbc038b6e5d74224627f5ba3be1cb47bc15","tid":248925,"uid":80570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:57:19.000Z","msg":"搵個仔做擋箭牌都幾撚低裝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n經常發表評論的時事評論員、網上媒體「謎米香港」創辦人之一蕭若元，昨日在其網台節目宣布，7月22日起不再評論香港和內地的時事及財經事務。<br />\n<br />\n蕭若元在節目《最新蕭析》表示，由7月22日起，不再評論香港和內地的時事及財經事務，「呢兩個地方唔存在」，並指是由於其兒子蕭定一的要求。<br />\n<br />\n他說，作為時事評論員20年，「要講嘅嘢都講晒，再講都係重複」，而節目將改名為「退休蕭析」，內容以旅遊、「八卦」、哲學、人生及外國時事為主。"},{"pid":"6b6d0b72832ab39e4af4cb0dc7306639df85a854","tid":248925,"uid":75765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T03:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本來以為熱普城出事可以畀腦燒狂抽水， 呢頭腦燒又自爆&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"33d6aaffec330b76c1cc481c819306544d4dc7c6","tid":248925,"uid":80570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T03:15:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本來以為熱普城出事可以畀腦燒狂抽水， 呢頭腦燒又自爆&hellip;&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪特登趁對面互屌緊  唔得閒屌佢呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f2f5f9335486381e3e88f132bdc0db8fff7b9d","tid":248925,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T03:20:51.000Z","msg":"以為唱歌嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62616f151fd712782e8405148cbfa3835b9588be","tid":248925,"uid":80570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T03:56:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為唱歌嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br 